title: Brooklyn Fundraiser for Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez
name: brooklyn-fundraiser-for-alexandria-ocasio-cortez
instructions: https://secure.actblue.com/donate/2411
description:
Calling all NYC progressives! Join Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez and Saikat Chakrabarti for a fundraiser to benefit her run for the House of Representatives!



Saikat Chakrabarti was Director of Organizing Technology for Bernie 2016, Executive Director of Justice Democrats, and in a previous life, a founding engineer at Stripe.



Learn from his experience and about why he is supporting Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez, New York City's foremost progressive congressional challenger.



Her exciting, grassroots campaign has been featured in outlets including the Wall Street Journal, The Nation, and NowThis Politics. 



This is a great opportunity for young professionals to meet and greet, for activists to support and get to know Alexandria, and for old friends to reconnect with Alexandria and her campaign!



Cherry Tree Bar, 65 4th Avenue,

Brooklyn, NY.

We will be knocking on doors of registered voters in the neighborhood to make sure they are aware of the June 26th Primary and to spread the word about Alexandria's inspiring run. We'll meet in the parking lot of P.C. Richards to go over the particulars and then talk to voters as they exit and enter the Taste of Sunnyside event. Anyone can help in this effort, no matter your age or experience. If you are a supporter of Ocasio2018, we want your help!  If you have questions you can reach out to your event host, Alena Acker, at 929-399-4179.
